00:27:38.100 --> 00:27:38.700
Ren Anle,

00:27:39.900 --> 00:27:40.660
en realidad eres

00:27:42.020 --> 00:27:42.900
el único accidente.

00:27:45.420 --> 00:27:46.700
¿El protagonista perfecto

00:27:47.020 --> 00:27:48.180
no convierte los accidentes en

00:27:48.180 --> 00:27:49.420
un logro?

00:27:52.020 --> 00:27:53.700
Lo acerté.

00:27:53.700 --> 00:27:54.940
¿Su Alteza está contento o no?

00:28:15.940 --> 00:28:18.860
[Contado Mutian]

00:28:26.220 --> 00:28:26.660
Ren Anle...

